---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<BaseLayout title="Now" description="Figure out what I'm currently doing!">
	<style>
		details > summary {
			cursor: pointer;
			list-style: none;
		}

		details > summary::before {
			content: "▶";
			margin-right: 0.5rem;
			transition: transform 100ms ease-in-out;
			display: inline-block;
		}

		details[open] > summary::before {
			transform: rotate(90deg);
		}
	</style>

	<h2 class="my-16 text-center text-3xl font-bold">Now</h2>
	<p class="-mt-12 text-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
		Last updated: <time datetime="2025-07-25">July 25, 2025</time>
	</p>

	<span
		class="prose-a:underline prose-a:transition hover:prose-a:text-blue-500 focus:prose-a:text-blue-500 active:prose-a:text-blue-500 prose-a:hover:prose-headings:text-blue-500"
	>
		<div class="mt-8">
			<h3 class="flex gap-1 text-2xl font-bold">
				<Icon name="tabler:headphones-filled" size={32} class="inline-block" /> Listening
			</h3>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
				<div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold">LP1 - FKA twigs</h3>
						<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-08-09"
							>August 09, 2025</time
						>
					</div>
					<p class="mt-1">
						Straight up ethereal experience. The instrumentals are simply malefic. The singing sent
						shivers down my spine. <strong>Lights On</strong> and <strong>Two Weeks</strong> made my
						eyes watery. You must listen to the whole thing, you must read the lyrics. Also, this woman
						is <em>FREAKY</em>!! 9/10.
					</p>
				</div>
				<details>
					<summary class="font-medium hover:text-blue-500">Older entries</summary>
					<div class="mt-2 space-y-4 border-gray-200 pl-4 dark:border-gray-700">
						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-between">
								<h3
									class="text-lg font-bold"
									aria-label="Alfredo 2 - Freddie Gibbs & The Alchemist"
								>
									Alfredo 2 - Freddie Gibbs & The Alchemist
								</h3>
								<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-08-08"
									>August 08, 2025</time
								>
							</div>
							<p class="mt-1">
								Did a full review in a <a href="/blog/alfredo-2-album-review">blog post</a>. 6/10.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-2 space-y-4 border-gray-200 pl-4 dark:border-gray-700">
						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-between">
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold" aria-label="Late Registration - Kanye West">
									Late Registration - Kanye West
								</h3>
								<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-07-28"
									>July 28, 2025</time
								>
							</div>
							<p class="mt-1">
								Starts off really strong. The song "Hey Mama" is a literal gem. While the production
								remains strong throughout the record, the lyrics and the delivery are not as good in
								the second half of the album. The skits are somewhat funny. Over all a pretty good
								album. 7/10.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-2 space-y-4 border-gray-200 pl-4 dark:border-gray-700">
						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-between">
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold" aria-label="Graduation - Kanye West">
									Graduation - Kanye West
								</h3>
								<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-07-27"
									>July 27, 2025</time
								>
							</div>
							<p class="mt-1">
								Amazing album. Masterfully mixed. Simply a classic. I've listened to it a bunch of
								time, and I'll continue to do so. I miss the old Kanye. 9/10.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-2 space-y-4 border-gray-200 pl-4 dark:border-gray-700">
						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-between">
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold" aria-label="DON’T TAP THE GLASS - Tyler, The Creator">
									DON’T TAP THE GLASS - Tyler, The Creator
								</h3>
								<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-07-25"
									>July 25, 2025</time
								>
							</div>
							<p class="mt-1">
								The album is quite nice! It is on the shorter side, and I wish it was a bit longer.
								Still, all the songs are great, so I just tend to put the whole thing on repeat
								throughout the day. I especially like how unserious, and silly it gets at times.
								8/10.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</details>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8">
			<h3 class="flex gap-1 text-2xl font-bold">
				<Icon name="tabler:device-tv-old" size={32} class="inline-block" /> Watching
			</h3>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
				<div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Hellsing (2001-2002)</h3>
						<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-07-25"
							>July 25, 2025</time
						>
					</div>
					<p class="mt-1">
						Watched it before, but I wanted to watch it again. I really like the idea behind this
						series. I really enjoy the characters. It's just that it ended abruptly and left a lot
						of stuff unresolved. I saw there are some other, more recent editions of the anime, so
						hopefully the newer ones deal with the unresolved stuff. For now 7/10.
					</p>
				</div>
