				<Icon name="tabler:book-filled" size={32} class="inline-block" /> Reading
			</h3>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
				<div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold">The Last Question - Isaac Asimov</h3>
						<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-07-25"
							>July 25, 2025</time
						>
					</div>
					<p class="mt-1">
						Short story, quite nice. Some concepts reminded me of <em>Logic Beach: Part I</em> by Exurb1a.
						It could be that Asimov's work was used as inspiration. Anyway, pretty good read. 7/10.
					</p>
				</div>
