				<Icon name="tabler:device-gamepad-3-filled" size={32} class="inline-block" /> Playing
			</h3>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
				<div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold" aria-label="Lorem Ipsum">A Hat in Time</h3>
						<time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" datetime="2025-07-25"
							>July 25, 2025</time
						>
					</div>
					<p class="mt-1">
						Quite ok 3D platformer game. It's not really my type of game tbh, but I still like to
						hop on it from time to time and complete a level or two. I'd give it around a 7/10.
					</p>
				</div>
